::Prowl::

Prowl nods in responce to Optimal Prime. "Do your best, yeah."

Then he turns to Mantle and nods. "Yeah, I was wondering if we could
use your ship to build a city after this battle, but from the
condition of it right now, I don't think we'll have much of a center
for it."

He taps his comm. "Epyon," he says into it, "There's some more
planning about the city where I'm at. You might wanna come here."
